      "body" : "I have a patch ready for this, but I'm not entirely sure about it. Perhaps another dev can take a look at it first!\nhttps://github.com/Diapolo/bitcoin/commit/04e75e4ab9e426b4b0c4e59196dbe5be127ad497\n\nI'm sure the current call to ``GetCredit(pcoin)`` can't be correct, as it does:\n<pre>\nif (IsCoinBase() && GetBlocksToMaturity() > 0)\n            return 0;\n</pre>\n\nAnd this is the opposite of what we need for the immature coins, right?",
